difficulty: It was easy when I could see the name of a column or row while looking at the piece of information I needed. It was difficult when I had to scroll to make sure I was looking at the right column or row.
format: If I could find the information quickly I was usually satisfied. I was unsatisfied when there was too much information in each cell. I was also unsatisfied when I needed to scroll to make sure I was looking at the correct column or row.
comments: I found them fairly easy, overall.
